{"tid":2012223,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一招KO 中共DQ參選人","createTime":"2020-05-11T13:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T18:16:47.000Z","uid":324193,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc2e9adf3357f5beb4959a69dde74c4f45ab98b","tid":2012223,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"預計中共黎緊會大規模DQ 立法會參選人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民主派本土派請準備定Plan B</span></span>，繼續參選係為左攞民意授權，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有民意支持先有得打國際線</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬一中共連Plan B 都DQ 或者出現舞弊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立即杯葛官方選舉同時自己搞公民議會投票</span></span>，如果公民議會有60%選民參加，官方選舉得30%藍絲玩，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際睇到邊面係民心所向，推動制裁又進一步</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25AE%25B5%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=7b4cffcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25AE%25B5%2F&h=30faf4e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5/</a><br />\n<br />\n作者FB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NoCagedMan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNoCagedMan%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=3ef971c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NoCagedMan/</a>"},{"pid":"6a19a90b674ff26c18f1af41c298b4fbc55f1ecf","tid":2012223,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"113a816f8419d17de5db8f3548302eac0d13722b","tid":2012223,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93561336c3b5e71bbc91b36cccb0cab52e359ede","tid":2012223,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"//在二零一九年一月，南美國家委內瑞拉的政局不穩，美國為首的五十國因官方選舉出現舞弊，改為承認之前在國會選舉勝出的反對派領袖瓜伊多為「總統」，跟原本執政的馬杜羅政府對抗，造成「一國兩總統」的僵持。委內瑞拉的情況包含複雜的地緣政治，相信類似情況未必會在香港重演，但北京會否打開這個可能一發不可收拾的潘朵拉盒子，親手製造一個「香港流亡議會」或者「香港流亡政府」出來，相信是北京一念之差。//"},{"pid":"dd5c17787daca6bab643e6e425a6e24dc1e23d04","tid":2012223,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"8cf05e00c720f5d85d15fe019cddeff9a10fbe13","tid":2012223,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"可以諗, 但要考慮以下問題<br />\n1. 自己搞公民議會會唔會違咗某D法?<br />\n2. 要預黑警搞事, 阻我地選<br />\n3. 選咗, 但無實權(無兵, 無官員, etc), 支共WFC"},{"pid":"01136b4bdda2fce7cbd39c734715ed5563a44a99","tid":2012223,"uid":324193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8cf05e00c720f5d85d15fe019cddeff9a10fbe13","tid":2012223,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"可以諗, 但要考慮以下問題<br />\n1. 自己搞公民議會會唔會違咗某D法?<br />\n2. 要預黑警搞事, 阻我地選<br />\n3. 選咗, 但無實權(無兵, 無官員, etc), 支共WFC"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:43: